ScalarVariable.description: Initial or guess value of state

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.imLeadLag.TF.a[2]
ScalarVariable.description: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.imLeadLag.TF.b[1]
ScalarVariable.description: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

ScalarVariable.description: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.imLeadLag.TF.initType
ScalarVariable.description: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3: initial state, 4: initial output)

ScalarVariable.description: Size of Denominator of transfer function.

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.imLeadLag.TF.nb
ScalarVariable.description: Size of Numerator of transfer function.

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.rotatingExciterLimited.sISO.initType
ScalarVariable.description: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3/4: initial output)

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition1
ScalarVariable.description: eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.state < eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.outMin and eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.K * eSDC1A.hV_GATE.p - eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.state > 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition2
ScalarVariable.description: eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.state > eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.outMax and eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.K * eSDC1A.hV_GATE.p - eSDC1A.simpleLagLim.state < 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.rotatingExciterLimited.sISO.limitsAtInit
ScalarVariable.description: = false, if limits are ignored during initialization (i.e., der(y)=k*u)

ScalarVariable.name: eSDC1A.rotatingExciterLimited.sISO.strict
ScalarVariable.description: = true, if strict limits with noEvent(..)
